      { id: 'D', text: 'Create a CloudWatch Event rule on your CodeCommit repository that reacts to pushes. As a target, choose an S3 bucket so that the code will be automatically zipped into S3. Create an S3 Event rule to trigger a Lambda function that will retrieve the zipped code from S3 and send it to the 3rd party API' }
