    stem: 'An online coding platform wants to fully customize the build tasks and automatically run builds concurrently to take the pain out of managing the build environments. The DevOps team at the company wants to use CodeBuild for all build-tasks and would like the artifacts created by CodeBuild to be named based on the branch being tested. The team wants this solution to be scalable to newer branches with a minimal amount of rework. As a DevOps Engineer, how would you go about implementing the simplest possible solution to address the given use-case?',
